<paragraph id="E260D53E4AED18A5FD07FC12378C2AD7" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">OMNH-P 43993, 21.7 mm SL, Hamahiga Island, off Okinawa Island, Ryukyu Islands, Japan, 250 m depth, 19 Sept. 2018, basket trap, K. Abe.</paragraph>
